			<div class="content" id="post-content-3629236">
									

<p>I can't shake the memory of Frank Reynolds from IASIP lying naked on the floor, covered in hand sanitizer, screaming &quot;I JUST WANTED TO BE PURE&quot;</p>
<p>No vote from me. It's a bit too.. cliche? for me. There's plenty of horror stories about people killing themselves due to wanting to get clean.</p>
<p>I didn't vote down because I thought this was well executed and well written, but the idea itself just felt overused to me. From this tale, it seems like you're a really good writer, and I think if you did a more original idea it'd do much better.</p>

